Beat Bobby Flay - Season 4, Episode 9




Out on a Limb

Breaking News: NBC's Tamron Hall and Chopped's Ted Allen are in the arena and Bobby is in their sights! They've brought two talented chefs to take him down; whiz kid Katherine Humphus gets into a culinary slugfest with the no-nonsense John Wassil, but who will make the headlines?
